{"tid":1235562,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"請將200萬民意帶到立法會選舉 (記得登記選民)","createTime":"2019-06-17T07:19:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T13:55:11.000Z","uid":120772,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6d7296b62fd0ef76061df1055ecbdbf49262fca3","tid":1235562,"uid":120772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T07:19:56.000Z","msg":"1. TVB狗已經開始動搖民意<br />\n又係一貫話今朝影響交通 搵幾條傻閪講到自己番唔到工 蝦佢地小市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記住佔中教我地既野 保住民意先<br />\n<br />\n2. 唔可以再重演過去幾年民主派既分化<br />\n難得今次勇武和理非大和解<br />\n其實兩邊做既野都有佢作用 要keep住 唔 好 割 蓆 <br />\n<br />\n3.目標轉向建制狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次好成功地見到建制同警犬不斷俾人割蓆<br />\n鍵盤戰士其實可以開始分化建制派選民 長輩圖一事 已經知道應該用咩方式<br />\n記得紀錄佢地呢幾日講左D咩 點割蓆 選舉日一定要拎番出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d0adba78caa1550cf5b2b63f9404b656af67dd8","tid":1235562,"uid":103759,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T13:55:11.000Z","msg":"[麻煩大家幫手share出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />] HK01妓者偷文死全家<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">幫老人家申請取消選民</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XZ6oPtB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXZ6oPtB.jpg&h=35e2103f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n郵遞（地址：香港灣仔港灣道25號海港中心10樓）<br />\n傳真（傳真號碼：2891 1180）<br />\n掃描表格後電郵至form@reo.gov.hk<br />\n掃描表格後上載至選舉事務處的電子表格上載平台（網址:<a href=\"http://www.reo-form.gov.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo-form.gov.hk&d=goC%2B%2BwCxwRgX8SEPTes0uyrXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=66553903\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.reo-form.gov.hk</a>）<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">新登記</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://